Advantage of using Prepared 
Statements
•
Regular Statement objects represent an SQL statement that must 
be compiled each time they are executed
•
It is often more convenient or more efficient to use a 
PreparedStatement object for sending SQL statements to the 
database. This special type of statement is derived from the 
Statement class 
•
PreparedStatement address the following requirements:
•
parameters can be substituted dynamically
•
values cannot always be represented as character strings
•
avoids repeated compiling of the same SQL statements

