Service()
Handles the setup and dispatching of doXXX()
doGet()
Handle GET class
Example: a document or an html page 
Additional information (or, a query string) can be appended to the GET method to refine the request 
doPost()
Handle POST request
Example: a credit card number, new data to be stored Sometimes megabytes of information can be sent 
Other predefined methods: doHead(), doTrace(), doOptions()

