From your program, you can send a message with different message types:
A - Abend; The message appears in a dialog box, and the program terminates.
E - Error; Depending on the program context, an error dialog appears or the program terminates.
I - Information; Appears in a dialog box, the system continues processing
S - Status; displayed along the footer; the system continues processing
W - Warning; Depending on the program context, an error dialog appears or the program terminates.
X - Exit; exits session processing
