Tag Element
•
<name>
•
Define the tag name "example"
•
<tag-class>
•
Define the full name of the tag handler class "ict.tag.ExampleTag”
•
<body-content>
•
empty 
•
The tag must NOT have a body.
•
scriptless
•
The tag must NOT have scripting elements (scriptlets, scripting 
expressions, and declarations), but it CAN have template text and EL and 
custom and standard actions.
•
tagdependent
•
The tag body is treated as plain text, so the EL is NOT evaluated and 
tags/actions are not triggered.
21

