Installing XAMPP /MAMP @)

XAMPP / MAMP - A local server environment with Web & MySQL server which supports PHP development.
Provide an easily-setup MySQL Server with GUI.
Comes with phpmyadmin portal for managing the server.
In this module, we will use the MySQL Server for JDBC connection with Java EE / Jarkata EE.

[Full Slide OCR]:
Why XAMPP/MAMP XAMPP / MAMP - A local server environment with Web & MySQL server which supports PHP development. Provide an easily-setup MySQL Server with GUI. Comes with phpmyadmin portal for managing the server. In this module, we will use the MySQL Server for JOBC connection with Java EE / Jarkata EE.

