@Autowired
@Autowired is an annotation used for dependency injection in Spring, which allows you to inject object dependencies implicitly. It can be placed on top of a field, setter method, or a constructor. Spring''s dependency injection mechanism will then inject the required bean into your class without the need for manual instantiation.

