@Bean
@Bean is an annotation used within a class annotated with @Configuration to declare a Spring bean. The method annotated with @Bean returns an object that Spring should manage as a bean in the application context. This is a way to programmatically define a component that Spring should manage and can be used to configure more complex dependencies.

