This paper contains FIVE questions.  
Answer ALL questions.   
Each question is worth TWENTY marks.  
 
Question 1 
 
 
You are the CEO of a PC game design company called Digital Realms (DR), which 
specializes in creating immersive and captivating gaming experiences. One of your clients is 
a renowned game publisher, Virtual Odyssey Studios (VOS), which is looking to develop a 
new fantasy role-playing game (RPG) set in a vast open world. 
 
(a) Your team has been tasked with designing new maps/levels for VOS’s new game, 
Galactic Wars. As work progresses, it becomes clear that there are multiple decisions 
needing to be made at different levels - strategic, tactical, and operational - to ensure 
this project succeeds.  
 
For each of the following questions that ask for different information for decisions, state 
the level of decision making they are trying to make: 
 
(i) Should the game, Galactic Wars, focus on developing games exclusively for 
PC/console or expand into mobile phones as well? 
(ii) Should we invest resources in expanding additional single-player campaign, or 
focus resources on new multiplayer modes/maps in the new game? 
(iii) What art style should we use on armor and weapons in our new game to create 
meaningful player expression and a sense of progression? 
(iv) After the new game has been launched, support requests will be increased 
dramatically. Should we prioritize hiring more live chat agents or developing an 
AI chatbot to handle routine queries? 
(v) Should we prioritize upgrading our game servers and backend systems or invest in 
new frontend tools and features to improve the player experience?          [5 marks] 
 
(b) DR is looking to implement the Marketing Mix to strengthen their marketing strategy 
and establish a significant market presence.  
(i) Name the 4P of Marketing Mix. 
(ii) Give one suggestion to any two sets of the 4P Marketing Mix for helping DR 
competitive in their market.   
[4 marks] 
 
 
(c) Customer Relationship Management (CRM) software is being implemented by DR to 
help manage relationships and interactions with game players.  
 
Suggest and briefly describe TWO features of CRM that help DR to improve the 
relationship with its customers (game players) and increase revenue. 
[6 marks] 
 
(d) DR is also considering the implementation of a Decision Support System (DSS) to 
enhance its management decision-making process. 
 
(i) What is the level of Decision Making that a DSS supports? Give one reason.  
[2 marks] 
(ii) Name three features of DSSs that help decision making in DR.  
[3 marks]

