Question 5 
 
A programmer from a fruit trading company plans to create an ABAP report for evaluating 
the fruit selling price.   
 
(a) The following shows the source code of a function module Z_FM_FRUIT_PRICE, 
which helps to calculate the selling price of the fruit. The module will raise an error 
when the cost is less than or equal to zero. Fill in the missing part (i) to (vi) to complete 
