JSP Directive Elements Specify attribute of the page itself type of content buffering requirements resources used how runtime errors should be handled Do not affect content of a response but how the container should handle it. Enclosed between <%@ %> Have a name and one or more attribute/value pairs attribute and values are case-sensitive enclosed in double quotes


