Wrap Up
•
Microservices vs monolithic application
•
Spring Boot – Standalone Application (Mini Server)
•
Controller / RestController – Similar to HttpServlet (map url to 
function)
•
Eureka Server – Naming Server for Service Discovery
•
REST Api + JSON – Standard for communication between 
microservices 
•
WebClient – Object for working with HTTP connection between 
microservices

